{"tid":689044,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好耐無好好瞓過覺？","createTime":"2018-06-03T18:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T08:50:56.000Z","uid":139763,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea4e10b0a51b1a4cde5fdc9bc5f166c66722e1c","tid":689044,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:41:59.000Z","msg":"細細個一落床即刻瞓到豬咁<br />\n唔知幾時開始一合埋眼個腦會係咁諗野<br />\n或者瞓唔著就玩手機<br />\n無原因咁失眠<br />\n明明好攰都無法入睡<br />\n<br />\n就算瞓到 第二日都好早醒<br />\n以前可以瞓成十幾個鐘<br />\n而家鬧鐘未叫醒你<br />\n你自己都醒左<br />\n<br />\n真係 好耐 好耐 無好好瞓過覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我大概係仲有牽掛先會咁。"},{"pid":"5dceaf8a67c79c31717b0065fbc12138789dbecd","tid":689044,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"又一個失眠夜"},{"pid":"4e492646cb5aa76400b50f35f2202c9f2ba57818","tid":689044,"uid":139763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:43:59.000Z","msg":"聽日仲要考試"},{"pid":"ed521a172e8e7c022a65a3e690b4a26803e71b46","tid":689044,"uid":96528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"明明好攰 強逼症咁唔比自己訓<br />\n第二朝例牌紮醒幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從失戀就係咁"},{"pid":"330879c5313ff4b3d7dc58330705df6cc6f7aac8","tid":689044,"uid":139763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed521a172e8e7c022a65a3e690b4a26803e71b46","tid":689044,"uid":96528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:45:11.000Z","msg":"明明好攰 強逼症咁唔比自己訓<br />\n第二朝例牌紮醒幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從失戀就係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T18:47:31.000Z","msg":"點解要強迫唔比自己訓.."},{"pid":"2f36585118a0f05908727531a75ae1623dac572a","tid":689044,"uid":48929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T19:05:56.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n近呢大半年都訓得好差<br />\n啲記憶力成pat屎咁"},{"pid":"ce923915a122a13b769b099ab161383ef8b8c3f7","tid":689044,"uid":399,"like":0,"disli